            "kicker": "OUR MISSION",
            "heading": "Our Mission",
            "text": "<p>JEMINISE was created with a simple mission: to make bedding feel more meaningful.</p><p>We design printed blankets, quilts, and comforters that are not only soft and comfortable, but also expressive. Whether it is a gift for someone you love, a seasonal refresh for your bedroom, or a design that reflects your personality, our products are made to turn ordinary spaces into warm, memorable places.</p><p>Every collection is thoughtfully created around comfort, emotion, and everyday use - helping you wrap yourself and your home in something that feels truly yours.</p>",
