            "image_alt": "",
            "image_position": "right",
            "kicker": "OUR STORY",
            "heading": "Our Story",
            "text": "<p>The idea behind JEMINISE began with one belief: a home feels warmer when the things inside it carry meaning.</p><p>Bedding is more than something we use at night. It is part of our routines, our memories, and the moments we share with family, friends, and even ourselves. A blanket can become a favorite gift. A quilt can bring personality to a room. A comforter can make the end of a long day feel softer.</p><p>That is why JEMINISE focuses on printed bedding designs that combine comfort with self-expression. From family-inspired pieces and faith-based designs to fantasy, floral, wildlife, sports, holiday, and book-lover collections, we create products for different stories, styles, and seasons of life.</p><p>Our goal is simple: to help every customer find a piece that feels personal, thoughtful, and comforting.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
