            "image_position": "left",
            "kicker": "OUR APPROACH",
            "heading": "Our Approach",
            "text": "<p>At JEMINISE, every design starts with the feeling we want it to bring.</p><p>Some pieces are made to feel calm and cozy. Some are playful, nostalgic, or meaningful. Others are designed to become thoughtful gifts for birthdays, holidays, memorial moments, family celebrations, or personal milestones.</p><p>We focus on creating bedding that is easy to love and easy to live with - soft textures, expressive artwork, and designs that fit naturally into bedrooms, dorm rooms, reading corners, guest spaces, and cozy nights at home.</p><p>JEMINISE is for anyone who believes comfort should be beautiful, personal, and full of feeling.</p>",
